469
00:27:39,347 --> 00:27:40,555
Oh.

470
00:27:40,659 --> 00:27:44,732
Ya, tentu, tapi mereka orang yang sangat baik.

471
00:27:44,835 --> 00:27:46,181
Sangat pintar juga.

472
00:27:46,285 --> 00:27:47,010
Terutama Maude.

473
00:27:47,113 --> 00:27:48,425
Ya.

474
00:27:48,528 --> 00:27:50,151
Tapi aku sering tak mengerti apa yang dia bicarakan.

475
00:27:50,254 --> 00:27:51,393
Aku juga.

476
00:27:54,258 --> 00:27:57,848
Aku sangat beruntung punya mereka.
Ya.

477
00:27:55,674 --> 00:27:57,848
Hmm.

478
00:27:57,952 --> 00:28:00,264
Mereka satu-satunya keluarga yang kupunya.

479
00:28:01,610 --> 00:28:03,095
Jadi...

480
00:28:04,613 --> 00:28:06,339
...Aku ingin bertemu mereka lagi.

